> Is onlyReturnExisting available in ACMEv1 or only ACMEv2?

@ohemorange `onlyReturnExisting` is only specified in ACMEv2. 

In ACMEv1 you can find an existing registration's ID by POSTing `newRegistration` with the existing keypair but there isn't any way to indicate to the server that you don't want a new reg. to be created if one doesn't exist.

